page.title: 12HOMES IN LYNEHAM
page.content: MOST OF THE CHILDREN LIVE IN R.A.F. QUARTERS ,THE REMAINDER LIVE IN COUNCIL OR PRIVATE HOUSING AT LYNEHAM BRADENSTOKE OR TOCKENHAM OR NEW ZEALAND. I LIVE IN TEAL AVE.IT IS AN R.A.F. HOUSE I HAVE A HALL AND A LOUNGE, A DINING ROOM AND WE HAVE GOT FRENCH WINDOWS. STEPHANIE MARSTON 7YRS. MY HOUSE HAS THREE BEDROOMS AND ME AND MY TWIN BROTHER HAVE A BEDROOM EACH.OUR KITCHEN IS BIG AND WE EAT IN IT MARTIN NOBLE 7YRS. I LIVE IN BRADENSTOKE AND MY HOUSE IS BIG IT HAS FOUR BEDROOMS. IHAVE GOT THREE SINKS AND TWO TOILETS .MY HOUSE IS VERY NICE. NEIL MURPHY 7YRS.
